author: By MATTHEW LEE AP Diplomatic Writer
title: Russia to the rescue? US, Moscow spar over aid deliveries
description: WASHINGTON (AP) — An odd new front in the U.S.-Russian rivalry has emerged as a Russian military cargo plane bearing a load of urgently needed medical supplies landed this week at New York’s JFK airport.
